description: Application for approval of reserved matters being access, appearance, landscaping, layout and scale  for Phases 2 and 3 to provide 219 residential dwellings following outline application ref. 15/00370/OUTM for the  re-development of the former Linpac Site comprising of up to 336 residential units in a mix of one, two, three and four bed houses and flats, up to 500 sqm of flexible A1/D1 floorspace, public open space (including children's playspace), associated landscaping and car parking.
